Entry.JapaneseText: 定期便以外にバルカへ渡る方法はないのか？
Entry.EnglishText: Is there any other way to get to Balka besides the liner service?

Entry.JapaneseText: <Mao>……さっきの兵士がこっちを見ている…… 変に勘繰られる前に港を離れたほうがよさそうだ。
Entry.EnglishText: <Mao>... The soldier from before is looking our way. We should leave the harbor before he gets suspicious.
